title: United Kingdom Imports - Toys, Games, Sports Requisites & Parts & Acces.
description: Imports - Toys, Games, Sports Requisites & Parts & Acces. in the United Kingdom increased to 726.85 GBP Million in September from 619.98 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports - Toys, Games, Sports Requisites & Parts & in the United Kingdom averaged 323.74 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 807.34 GBP Million in November of 2021 and a record low of 122.88 GBP Million in February of 2003.
